key_conclusion:
Bloody Stream is written in the key of C Minor.  

According to the Theorytab database, it is the 3rd most popular key among Minor keys and     the 9th most popular  among all keys. The three most important chords, built off the 1st, 4th and 5th scale degrees are all minor chords (C minor, F minor, and G minor).
